Name: Make Them Naked
About the game: Welcome to Make Them Naked! It's a cute and relaxing game that offers you four different characters to undress. Make a cup of tea and dive into the world of love! The game allows you to play with one hand thanks to an easy control. Each girl has a different personality and preferences: Wendy - a shy girl who doesn't like rude people. Yuka - a life of the party who loves joking. Natsumi - a mystery of this world. It'll be a challenge to undress her. Aurora - a dominant one. Aren't you scared? Choose correct dialogue options to seduce your companion. Click the circles to the beat! We wish you to have a good time. We'd be delighted if you leave a review about this game.
